Sentencas: CSZM compounds were synthesized by dry chemistry route with 5, 10, and 15% dopant of Mg dopants in the Ce0.8-2x Sm-0.2 Zr-x Mg-x O2-d, {x = 0.05, 0.1 & 0.15}.

Sentencas: The newly investigated materials were physically, chemically, and electrochemically studied and have shown promising results.

Sentencas: The CSZM was crystalized in a fluorite structure with a pure cubic phase in a space group Fm3m and cell parameter a = 5.401742 degrees A and theoretical density from 7.6 to 8.9 after firing in the air with a final temperature of 1400 degrees C.
